Stroboscopic Photo Technique
In this case, I've used TWO lights on two different Broncolor Scoro S 3200 power packs  in order to set the lights in different fire patterns. The first stripbox behind me (aka the model :D ) was set in the sequence mode to fire 8 times as the rim light to separate me from the background. The second stripbox in front of me as the main light was set in the delay mode to fire at the same time with the 8th fire of the rim light stripbox to illuminate my last move sharply. Triggered remotely.
